---
layout: base.njk
title: RSVP Confirmed - Golden Wings Screening
description: Your RSVP for the Golden Wings documentary screening has been confirmed
---

{% set event = siteConfig.event %}
{% set form = siteConfig.form %}
{% set theme = siteConfig.theme %}

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-green-50 to-white flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-12">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <svg class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">You're All Set for Takeoff!</h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Your RSVP for <strong>{{ event.title }}</strong> has been confirmed. {{ form.successMessage }}
      </p>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8 text-left">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">Event Details</h2>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ event.date }}</p>
          <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{ event.timePST }} PST / {{ event.timeCST }} CST / {{ event.timeEST }} EST</p>
          <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{ event.duration }}</p>
          <p><strong>Venue:</strong> {{ event.venue }}</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4">Your boarding pass will arrive 24 hours before the screening.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 supporting-copy">
        {{ theme.missionStatement }} We can't wait to share Robyn Stewart's sky-high legacy with you.
      </p>

      <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-900 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all">
        Return to Home
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
